data.description: Welcome to your new home in historic Macon, GA! This charming residence boasts 1,224 square feet of well-utilized space, offering a surprising punch of comfort and functionality in every corner. With 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, including a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, privacy is never an issue. The heart of the home lies in its open living area seamlessly connected to the kitchen, creating an inviting and spacious atmosphere for gatherings and daily living. Step outside to the privacy-fenced backyard, perfect for relaxation or outdoor activities in complete seclusion. Built just 5 years ago, this home presents a myriad of possibilities for various buyers, whether you're an investor seeking a promising opportunity, a first-time homebuyer starting your journey, or someone looking to downsize without compromising on quality. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your own. Call today to schedule a private showing and embark on the next chapter of your life in this delightful Macon residence.
